<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01//EN"
        "http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="en">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <title></title>
    #parse("comm/head.vm")
    <link href="#springUrl('/resource/css/account/rechargeStep2.css')" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
<div class="content">
    <div class="recharge_header"><a href="#springUrl('/account.htm')">账户资产></a><a href="#springUrl('/recharge.htm')">充值></a><span>充值支付</span></div>
        <div class="nav">
        <div class="left">
            <p class="leftP1">
                <span class="leftP1_span1">充值金额：</span>
                <span class="leftP1_span2">$!{xtr.money($rechargeData.rechargeMoney)}</span>
                <span class="leftP1_span3">元</span>
            </p>
            <p class="leftP2">
                <span class="leftP2_span1">订单类型：</span>
                <span class="leftP2_span2">充值订单</span>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
            <p class="rightP1">
                <span class="rightP1_span1">订单编号:</span>
                <span class="rightP1_span2">$!{rechargeData.rechargeNumber}</span>
            </p>
            <p class="rightP2">
                <span class="rightP2_span1">订单创建时间：</span>
                <span class="rightP2_span2">$!date.format('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss',$rechargeData.rechargeAddtime)</span>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hint">
        <h2>重要提示请仔细阅读，阅读完毕后点击“我已阅读完毕”，显示收款银行账户</h2>
        <p>1、请复制订单编号到汇款备注栏中：<span>$!rechargeData.rechargeNumber</span></p>
        <p>2、如果对多个订单进行合并付款，则复制多个订单编号到汇款备注栏中，且将多个订单用逗号隔开</p>
        <p>如：412616000622151,412616400632153</p>
        <p>3、一般线下汇款确认到账时间为<span>一至两个工作日，节假日除外</span>请耐心等待，如有疑问请联系400-175-8090</p>
        <div class="end"><input type="checkbox" id="ckbox"><label for="ckbox">我已阅读完毕</label></div>
    </div>
    <div class="message">
        <div class="bank" style="padding-top:30px;">
            <div class="bank1">银行：</div>
            <div class="bank2">中国银行</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bank">
            <div class="bank1">账户名称：</div>
            <div class="bank2">网银在线（北京）科技有限公司客户备付金</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bank">
            <div class="bank1">账号：</div>
            <div class="bank2">341561371394</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bank">
            <div class="bank1">开户支行：</div>
            <div class="bank2">中国银行股份有限公司北京奥运村支行</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom"><input type="button" value="确定" id="btn" disabled="disabled" style="background:#ccc;"></div>
    <form>

    </form>
</div>
</body>
<script>


    RechargeStep2Extend = {
        submitForm : function(){
            window.location.href = BASE_PATH + '/rechargeSuccess.htm?rechargeId=' + $!{rechargeData.rechargeId};
        }
    }
    $(function() {

        $("#ckbox").click(function() {
            if ($('#ckbox').prop('checked')) {
                $('.message').show();
                $("#btn").removeAttr("disabled").css('background','#0696fa');
            } else {
                $('.message').hide();
                $("#btn").attr({"disabled":"disabled"}).css('background','#ccc');
            }
        })

        $("#btn").click(function() {
            RechargeStep2Extend.submitForm();
        });

    })



</script>
</html>